}</h2>"},"ya5.1.2:1.0.2":{"pli":"5.1.2.1.1. Anuloma ","html":"<h3>{}</h3>"},"ya5.1.2:1.1":{"pli":"Dukkhaṁ dukkhasaccanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:2.1":{"pli":"Dukkhasaccaṁ dukkhanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:3.1":{"pli":"Kāyikaṁ dukkhaṁ cetasikaṁ dukkhaṁ ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ dukkhasaccaṁ, na dukkhaṁ. Kāyikaṁ dukkhaṁ cetasikaṁ dukkhaṁ dukkhañceva dukkhasaccañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:4.1":{"pli":"Samudayo samudayasaccanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:5.1":{"pli":"Samudayasaccaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso samudayo, na samudayasaccaṁ. Samudayasaccaṁ samudayo ceva samudayasaccañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:6.1":{"pli":"Samudayasaccaṁ samudayoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:7.1":{"pli":"Nirodho nirodhasaccanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:8.1":{"pli":"Nirodhasaccaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso nirodho, na nirodhasaccaṁ. Nirodhasaccaṁ nirodho ceva nirodhasaccañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:9.1":{"pli":"Nirodhasaccaṁ nirodhoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:10.1":{"pli":"Maggo maggasaccanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:11.1":{"pli":"Maggasaccaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso maggo, na maggasaccaṁ. Maggasaccaṁ maggo ceva maggasaccañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:12.1":{"pli":"Maggasaccaṁ maggoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:13.0":{"pli":"5.1.2.1.2. Paccanīka ","html":"<h3>{}</h3>"},"ya5.1.2:13.1":{"pli":"Na dukkhaṁ na dukkhasaccanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:14.1":{"pli":"Kāyikaṁ dukkhaṁ cetasikaṁ dukkhaṁ ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na dukkhaṁ dukkhasaccaṁ. Dukkhañca dukkhasaccañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva dukkhaṁ na ca dukkhasaccaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:15.1":{"pli":"Na dukkhasaccaṁ na dukkhanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:16.1":{"pli":"Na samudayo na samudayasaccanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:17.1":{"pli":"Na samudayasaccaṁ na samudayoti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:18.1":{"pli":"Samudayasaccaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso na samudayasaccaṁ, samudayo. Samudayañca samudayasaccañca ṭhapetvā avaseso na ceva samudayo na ca samudayasaccaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:19.1":{"pli":"Na nirodho na nirodhasaccanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:20.1":{"pli":"Na nirodhasaccaṁ na nirodhoti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:21.1":{"pli":"Nirodhasaccaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso na nirodhasaccaṁ, nirodho. Nirodhañca nirodhasaccañca ṭhapetvā avaseso na ceva nirodho na ca nirodhasaccaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:22.1":{"pli":"Na maggo na maggasaccanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:23.1":{"pli":"Na maggasaccaṁ na maggoti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:24.1":{"pli":"Maggasaccaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso na maggasaccaṁ, maggo. Maggañca maggasaccañca ṭhapetvā avaseso na ceva maggo na ca maggasaccaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:25.0.1":{"pli":"5.1.2.2. Padasodhanamūlacakkavāra ","html":"<h2>{}</h2>"},"ya5.1.2:25.0.2":{"pli":"5.1.2.2.1. Anuloma ","html":"<h3>{}</h3>"},"ya5.1.2:25.1":{"pli":"Dukkhaṁ dukkhasaccanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:26.1":{"pli":"Saccā samudayasaccanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:27.1":{"pli":"Samudayasaccaṁ saccañceva samudayasaccañca. Avasesā saccā na samudayasaccaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:28.1":{"pli":"Dukkhaṁ dukkhasaccanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:29.1":{"pli":"Saccā nirodhasaccanti? …pe… Saccā maggasaccanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:30.1":{"pli":"Maggasaccaṁ saccañceva maggasaccañca. Avasesā saccā na maggasaccaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya5.1.2:31.1":{"pli":"Samudayo samudayasaccanti? ","html":"<p data-directio